George Orwell:
Birthplace - East Champaran, Bihar, India
DOB/DOD - June 25, 1903 - January 21, 1950
List of Major Works - Animal Farm, Nineteen Eighty-Four, Homage to Catalonia, Down and Out in Paris and London
Alma Mater - Eton College
List of Major Awards - Prometheus Hall of Fame Award, Retro Hugo Award

J.R.R. Tolkien:
Birthplace - Bloemfontein, Free State, South Africa
DOB/DOD - January 3 1892 - September 2 1973
List of Major Works - The Lord of the Rings, The Hobbit, The Silmarillion, Unfinished Tales
Alma Mater - Exeter College
List of Major Awards - International Fantasy Award, Prometheus Hall of Fame Award, Locus Award for Best Fantasy Novel

F. Scott Fitzgerald:
Birthplace - St. Paul, Minnesota, United States
DOB/DOD - September 24, 1896 - December 21, 1940 
List of Major Works - The Great Gatsby, Tender is the Night, The Last Tycoon, This Side of Paradise
Alma Mater - Princeton University
List of Major Awards - New Jersey Hall of Fame